      "question": "A local community garden is rectangular in shape. The total area of the garden is $300 \\text{ m}^2$. The length of the garden is $7 \\text{ m}$ more than its breadth. Let the breadth of the garden be $x$ metres. Based on this information, solve the following questions.",
