              "Factorize: $x(x + 20) - 15(x + 20) = 0$.",
              "Solve: $(x - 15)(x + 20) = 0$."
            ],
            "derivation": "$x^2 + 20x - 15x - 300 = 0 \\\\ x(x + 20) - 15(x + 20) = 0 \\\\ (x - 15)(x + 20) = 0 \\\\ x = 15, x = -20$"
